                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-download-wrapper">
                                <span class="logo-description">당신의 삶에 인테리어를 그리다</span>
                                <img src="https://static.gridazip.co.kr/assets/images_renewal/logo_g.png" alt="그리다집 로고" />

                                <div class="contact-info">
